{"tid":303433,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇ching唔要冷氣機可以讓俾我","createTime":"2017-06-30T07:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T07:57:14.000Z","uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cd797d2a193634f45ea0507ca8386892f801e82f","tid":303433,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:46:18.000Z","msg":"利申左先 屋企冇乜錢買冷氣機<br />\r\n唔係話窮到穿窿 但就算有多餘錢都唔係去買焗爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n我黎緊想去涼冷氣 買個冷氣機幾千蚊好似唔太貴<br />\r\n但屋企唔太多錢 幾千蚊食到一個星期了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n所以睇下有冇巴絲有d全新/新淨ge二手冷氣機讓出黎<br />\r\n送比我就當然最好 但如果係平平地放比我我都唔介意嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n希望各位巴絲幫幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果有野想交換可以問下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n祝各位回歸快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 回歸願望除左香港繁榮 港獨倒台之外<br />\r\n其中一個細細地ge願望就係想自己有個出到冷風既冷氣機 等自己生活冇咁濕熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a4bd42bf671236c3eeb784bb42e3352bfaf8a5","tid":303433,"uid":2470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:47:18.000Z","msg":"電費好貴 落街涼啦 咁多商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3819f139373e16bf1d1e45a188834df9ca352aa6","tid":303433,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:47:38.000Z","msg":"你自己上黎拆上黎抬ok?我換新"},{"pid":"4357291b7ce31e687e94edaf5da4aca59335c2d4","tid":303433,"uid":106460,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:47:50.000Z","msg":"You up mud 9?"},{"pid":"3790b55f4ace63d0c223106e02bb6aa2307a7975","tid":303433,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-